Class GenericStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • com.scar.android.Fragments.GenericStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, StoreFrag

    public class GenericStore
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements StoreFrag
    A generic store for adding in any details about a server This includes:
    1. A label
    2. A hostname
    3. A port
    4. username infomation
    5. password informatiom
    Note: all details from these stores are stored in the encrypted meta database
